data.enText: a strip of leather, cloth or other material that is used to fasten sth, keep sth in place, carry sth or hold onto sth
the shoulder straps of her dress
a watch with a leather strap
to fasten sb/sth in place using a strap or straps
He strapped the knife to his leg.

data.chText: 所有东西必须绑定，免得来回滑动。
data.enText: Everything had to be strapped down to stop it from sliding around.
Are you strapped in (= wearing a seat belt in a car, plane, etc.) ?
to wrap strips of material around a wound or an injured part of the body

data.chText: 我的腿必须打六星期绷带。
data.enText: I have to keep my leg strapped up for six weeks.

tr: whip consisting of a strip of leather used in flogging
an elongated leather strip (or a strip of similar material) for binding things together or holding something in position
a band that goes over the shoulder and supports a garment or bag
hanger consisting of a loop of leather suspended from the ceiling of a bus or train
secure (a sprained joint) with a strap
beat severely with a whip or rod
example: The teacher often flogged the students

value.def: A strap is a narrow piece of leather, cloth, or other material. Straps are used to carry things, fasten things together, or to hold a piece of clothing in place.

example.ex: Nancy gripped the strap of her beach bag...
example.tran: 南希抓住了自己沙滩包的带子。

example.ex: Brian pulled the straps through the buckles of his suitcase...
example.tran: 布赖恩将带子穿过自己手提箱的带扣。

example.ex: She pulled the strap of her nightgown onto her shoulder...
example.tran: 她将自己睡袍的吊带拉到肩膀上。

value.def: If you strap something somewhere, you fasten it there with a strap.

example.ex: Strapping the skis on the roof, we boarded the hovercraft in Dover...
example.tran: 用带子把滑水板绑在船顶后，我们就在多佛登上了气垫船。

example.ex: She strapped the gun belt around her middle...
Through the basement window I saw him strap on his pink cycling helmet...
example.tran: 透过地下室的窗户，我看到他正在把他那粉色的自行车头盔系在头上。

example.ex: The carer will have to do all the work: placing the patient on the seat, strapping him in, taking him off again at the top.
example.tran: 护工将要全程照顾：将病人抱到座位上，替他系好安全带，到顶层后再将他抱下来。
